<html>
  <head>
    <title>Register</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <a href="/login">Login</a>

    <h1>Please ask for registration</h1>
    This is a demo installation of ClimDaPs. If you want to try it out please do the following steps:
    <ol>
      <li>
        Get an OpenID Account at an ESGF Node, 
        for example at <a href="http://esgf-data.dkrz.de">http://esgf-data.dkrz.de</a>
      </li>
      <li>
        To be allowed to download data from ESGF (e.a. CORDEX) you
        must be registered in the <em>non-commercial</em> ESGF
        Group. You can register for this group by just downloading data
        files from an <a href="http://esgf-data.dkrz.de">ESGF
        Node</a>. When you are not registered you will be asked for
        group registration once.
      </li>
      <li>
        Finally to get registered for this demo application, 
        please send <a href="mailto:nils.hempelmann@hzg.de">Nils Hempelmann</a> 
        from Climate Service Center (CSC) a short eMail with the following information:
        <ul>
          <li>The eMail address of your ESGF OpenID Account</li>
          <li>Some words why you would like to use this ClimDaPs Demo</li>
          <li>Where did you hear from this ClimDaPs Demo?</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
    </ol>

    <div tal:condition="email">
      <h2>Your email Address for registration is</h2>
      ${email}<br/>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
